OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny wintry showers in northeast
OL,6,FScotland will ease during the early
OL,7,Fmorning. Most areas stay dry and
OL,8,Fbright before clouds, rain, and
OL,9,Fstrengthening winds reach Northern
OL,10,FIreland and western Scotland later.
OL,11,FMilder than Wednesday, but still
OL,12,Ffeeling rather cold.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA milder night with
OL,15,Fwidespread cloud and rain, heavy over
OL,16,Fwestern hills. The southeast may stay
OL,17,Fclearer with patchy frost. Clearer
OL,18,Fskies and showers reach northwest
OL,19,FScotland later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
