OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FRain returns on Friday and
OL,6,Fpushed southeastwards through the day.
OL,7,FSunnier skies in the north, but cooler
OL,8,Fonce again with some wintry showers
OL,9,Fand stronger gusts of winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
